  |
  |<--- 'sg_dma_address(sg) - sg->offset'
  |               .------ sg_dma_address(sg)
  |              |  .---- sg_dma_len(sg)
  |<-sg->offset->|  |
  V              |<-->|    Another one cpu page
  +----+----+----+----+   +----+----+----+----+
  |xxxx|         ||||||   |||||||||||||||||||||
  +----+----+----+----+   +----+----+----+----+
  ^                   ^   ^                   ^
  |<---   da_len  --->|   |                   |
  |                   |   |                   |
  |    .--------------'   |                   |
  |    | .----------------'                   |
  |    | |                   .----------------'
  |    | |                   |
  |    | +----+----+----+----+
  |    | |||||||||||||||||||||
  |    | +----+----+----+----+
  |    |
  |    '--------------.  da_len = sg_dma_len(sg) + sg->offset, using
